data.description: Ideal Miner Crest Location!  Loads of room in this 5bd/3bath home on cul de sac. Beautiful(nonfuctional)rock fireplace is the focal point of the large living room. 8x16 sun porch is perfect for plants or play area and extends living space. Updated kitchen boosts granite, decorative tile, ss appliances, double ovens and refaced cabinets. Lower level is roomy and has a kitchenette,separate entrance, wood burning fireplace and 2 bed 1 bath. Wonderful home in established Milner Crest neighborhood.
